    <item>
      <title>墨西哥暗示将对特朗普的关税威胁采取报复措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/mexico-hints-at-retaliation-after-trump-threatens-steep-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·辛鲍姆表示，墨西哥可以采取征税措施来回应唐纳德·特朗普威胁的关税，并警告称，这样做的经济后果将是可怕的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/mexico-hints-at-retaliation-after-trump-threatens-steep-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 14:52:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金早盘因特朗普关税威胁而下跌，目前持稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/gold-falls-as-trump-tariff-threat-on-canada-mexico-aids-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普威胁对加拿大和墨西哥征收 25% 的进口关税，美元上涨，金价早盘下跌，之后趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/gold-falls-as-trump-tariff-threat-on-canada-mexico-aids-dollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 00:32:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
